Customer Purchase Behavior Dashboard (Power BI)
📊 Overview

This project analyzes customer purchasing behavior using Power BI. The dashboard provides insights into revenue trends, customer demographics, and category performance.

🚀 Key Insights
Total revenue reached $233K
Clothing generated the highest sales among all categories
Average customer spending is $59.76
Seasonal trends show variation in purchasing behavior across Fall, Spring, Summer, and Winter
📈 Features
Interactive filters (Gender, Category, Location, Season)
KPI cards for quick business overview
Customer segmentation by purchase frequency
Category-level revenue analysis
🛠 Tools Used
Power BI
Data Cleaning & Transformation
Data Visualization

📌 Business Value

This dashboard helps stakeholders understand customer behavior and optimize product strategy, pricing, and marketing campaigns.
